{
  "text": "EPCs were washed with PBS and gently detached with 0.5 mmol/L EDTA in PBS. After centrifugation and resuspension in basal complete medium supplemented with 5% FCS, identical cell numbers (10 5 /well) were placed onto fibronectin-coated culture dishes and incubated for 30 min at 378C. [CITATION_1] Adherent cells were counted by two independent blinded investigators.",
